BlackMarbleViewer requires the following Python libraries

pip install blackmarblepy
pip install colorcet contextily geopandas matplotlib seaborn pandas folium mapclassify

BlackMarbleViewer requires using NASA Earthdata bearer token. To obtain a token, please follow the steps below:

Go to [the NASA LAADS Archive](https://ladsweb.modaps.eosdis.nasa.gov/archive/allData/5000/VNP46A3/)
Click "Login" (bottom on top right); create an account if needed.
In Your Account Information Click "Generate Token"
The Token must be depositet in the GUI